author: marrs
msg: Added a test that validates service dependency injection of both normal and named members.

author: marrs
msg: Slightly relaxed the rules for member injection when using a named field. In that case it is now enough to have a field that is of an assignable type, instead of requiring an exact type.

author: kahatlen
msg: DERBY-4650: Predicates in HAVING clause should be pushed down to restricted VTIs
Added a test case that shows that a predicate is not pushed down.
